videos.description: Dylan Smith lobs up the alley-oop to Deandre Ayton who throws down the two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Ayton slams the alley-oop dunk

videos.description: Deandre Ayton spins into the paint then gets the hook shot to go plus the foul.
videos.headline: Ayton powers in for the and-1

videos.description: Arizona gets multiple offensive rebounds on one possession that lead to a putback layup from Dusan Ristic.
videos.headline: Fight for rebounds ends with Arizona bucket

videos.description: Nick Rakocevic makes some good post moves to get the open look for a hook shot.
videos.headline: USC's Rakocevic with the nice hook shot

videos.description: Parker Jackson-Cartwright passes to a wide-open Deandre Ayton on the inbounds pass who slams the two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Ayton throws down dunk off inbounds pass

videos.description: Parker Jackson-Cartwright gets the steal on one end of the court setting up Allonzo Trier to drive the baseline for the reverse layup.
videos.headline: Arizona steal leads to Trier reverse layup

videos.description: Elijah Stewart blocks the shot then follows it up with a quick fast-break layup on the other end.
videos.headline: Stewart gets the block and fast-break layup for USC

videos.description: Deandre Ayton loses control of the ball for a moment but stays with it to get the bucket plus the foul.
videos.headline: Ayton stays with ball for and-1 score

videos.description: Jordan McLaughlin lobs up the alley-oop to Chimezie Metu who slams the huge two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Trojans connect on massive alley-oop

videos.description: Deandre Ayton passes to a driving Rawle Alkins who throws down the massive two-handed slam over the USC defender.
videos.headline: Arizona's Alkins posterizes USC defender

videos.description: Deandre Ayton follows up the massive dunk from Rawle Alkins with another two-handed slam himself.
videos.headline: Ayton slams alley-oop dunk

videos.description: Dusan Ristic lobs up another oop for Deandre Ayton who makes the two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Ayton throws down another alley-oop

videos.description: Parker Jackson-Cartwright throws up another alley-oop for Deandre Ayton who slams it down.
videos.headline: Ayton with one more alley-oop slam
